desc
@C program to use modbus to grab state information from the sunsaver smart charger.
@


1.7
log
@replace ASCII degree symbol with the HTML equiv of the same.
@
text
@//$Id: sunsaver.c,v 1.6 2011/06/21 00:52:13 wschaub Exp wschaub $
